{"title":"Go日志轮转方案","uid":"af48ff0c803acb4eef8ee9f0941c4a2e","slug":"2025-12-14-01","date":"2025-12-14T21:28:55.000Z","updated":"2025-12-14T13:30:18.575Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2025-12-14-01.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"上代码\"><a href=\"#上代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"上代码\"></a>上代码</h2><p>直接调用<code>NewLogger</code>函数初始化日志实例就行,参数是日志的保存位置,随便改改就能用了.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight go\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> logger</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">&quot;os&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">&quot;time&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">&quot;go.uber.org/zap&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">&quot;go.uber.org/zap/zapcore&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">&quot;gopkg.in/natefinch/lumberjack.v2&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Logger 封装 zap.SugaredLogger，提供带轮转功能的日志记录器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> Logger <span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// sugar 是 zap 提供的语法糖 logger，支持 printf 风格的格式化输出 (Info, Infof 等)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsugar *zap.SugaredLogger</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// rotator 保存 lumberjack 实例，用于在 Close 时显式关闭文件句柄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\trotator *lumberjack.Logger</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// NewLogger 初始化日志模块</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// logDir: 日志文件保存的目录 (例如 &quot;./logs&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">NewLogger</span><span class=\"params\">(logDir <span class=\"type\">string</span>)</span></span> (*Logger, <span class=\"type\">error</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 1. 配置 Lumberjack (日志切割/轮转核心)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 它是 zap 的底层输出目标 (WriteSyncer)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\trotator := &amp;lumberjack.Logger&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tFilename:   logDir + <span class=\"string\">&quot;/app.log&quot;</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// 日志文件的完整路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tMaxSize:    <span class=\"number\">10</span>,                  <span class=\"comment\">// 单个日志文件的最大体积，单位：MB</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tMaxBackups: <span class=\"number\">30</span>,                  <span class=\"comment\">// 最多保留的历史日志文件个数 (旧文件会被删除)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tMaxAge:     <span class=\"number\">30</span>,                  <span class=\"comment\">// 最多保留的历史日志天数 (旧文件会被删除)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tCompress:   <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,                <span class=\"comment\">// 是否压缩旧日志 (保存为 .gz 格式以节省空间)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tLocalTime:  <span class=\"literal\">true</span>,                <span class=\"comment\">// 备份文件名是否使用本地时间 (默认是 UTC)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 2. 配置 Zap 的日志编码格式 (Encoder)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 这里决定了日志在文件中长什么样</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tencoderConfig := zapcore.EncoderConfig&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tTimeKey:        <span class=\"string\">&quot;time&quot;</span>,                         <span class=\"comment\">// 时间字段的 key 名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tLevelKey:       <span class=\"string\">&quot;level&quot;</span>,                        <span class=\"comment\">// 级别字段的 key 名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tNameKey:        <span class=\"string\">&quot;logger&quot;</span>,                       <span class=\"comment\">// logger 名称字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tCallerKey:      <span class=\"string\">&quot;caller&quot;</span>,                       <span class=\"comment\">// 调用者代码行号字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tMessageKey:     <span class=\"string\">&quot;msg&quot;</span>,                          <span class=\"comment\">// 消息内容字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tStacktraceKey:  <span class=\"string\">&quot;stacktrace&quot;</span>,                   <span class=\"comment\">// 堆栈跟踪字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tLineEnding:     zapcore.DefaultLineEnding,      <span class=\"comment\">// 换行符 (\\n)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tEncodeLevel:    zapcore.CapitalLevelEncoder,    <span class=\"comment\">// 级别格式: 大写 (INFO, ERROR)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tEncodeTime:     customTimeEncoder,              <span class=\"comment\">// 时间格式: 自定义函数 (见下方)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tEncodeDuration: zapcore.SecondsDurationEncoder, <span class=\"comment\">// 执行消耗时间格式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tEncodeCaller:   zapcore.ShortCallerEncoder,     <span class=\"comment\">// 调用者格式: 包名/文件名:行号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 3. 创建 Core (核心逻辑)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// NewMultiWriteSyncer 允许我们将日志同时输出到 [文件] 和 [控制台]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\twriteSyncer := zapcore.NewMultiWriteSyncer(</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tzapcore.AddSync(rotator),   <span class=\"comment\">// 输出到文件 (带轮转)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tzapcore.AddSync(os.Stdout), <span class=\"comment\">// 输出到控制台 (方便开发调试)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcore := zapcore.NewCore(</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tzapcore.NewConsoleEncoder(encoderConfig), <span class=\"comment\">// 使用 Console 编码器 (人类可读性更好，不像 JSON 那么乱)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\twriteSyncer,                              <span class=\"comment\">// 输出位置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tzapcore.InfoLevel,                        <span class=\"comment\">// 日志级别 (Info 及以上才记录)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 4. 构建 Logger 实例</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// AddCaller: 显示日志是哪一行代码打出来的</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// AddCallerSkip(1): 关键点！因为我们封装了一层 Logger 结构体，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 如果不跳过 1 层，所有日志显示的行号都会是 logger.go 中的 Info 函数，而不是业务代码的位置。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tzapLogger := zap.New(core, zap.AddCaller(), zap.AddCallerSkip(<span class=\"number\">1</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &amp;Logger&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tsugar:   zapLogger.Sugar(), <span class=\"comment\">// 使用 Sugar 模式，支持 Infof 这种 printf 风格</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\trotator: rotator,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;, <span class=\"literal\">nil</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// customTimeEncoder 自定义时间格式化 (例如: 2025-12-14 22:30:05.123)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">customTimeEncoder</span><span class=\"params\">(t time.Time, enc zapcore.PrimitiveArrayEncoder)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tenc.AppendString(t.Format(<span class=\"string\">&quot;2006-01-02 15:04:05.000&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Info 对应原有的 Info 方法，支持 formatting</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"params\">(l *Logger)</span></span> Info(format <span class=\"type\">string</span>, v ...<span class=\"keyword\">interface</span>&#123;&#125;) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// Infof 内部自动处理 fmt.Sprintf，不需要你手动 format</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tl.sugar.Infof(format, v...)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Error 对应原有的 Error 方法</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"params\">(l *Logger)</span></span> Error(format <span class=\"type\">string</span>, v ...<span class=\"keyword\">interface</span>&#123;&#125;) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tl.sugar.Errorf(format, v...)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Warn 对应原有的 Warn 方法</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"params\">(l *Logger)</span></span> Warn(format <span class=\"type\">string</span>, v ...<span class=\"keyword\">interface</span>&#123;&#125;) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tl.sugar.Warnf(format, v...)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Close 在程序退出时调用，确保缓冲区日志刷入磁盘</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"params\">(l *Logger)</span></span> Close() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// Sync 刷新缓冲区</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t_ = l.sugar.Sync()</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 关闭文件句柄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> l.rotator != <span class=\"literal\">nil</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t_ = l.rotator.Close()</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","feature":false,"text":"上代码直接调用NewLogger函数初始化日志实例就行,参数是日志的保存位置,随便改改就能用了. 1234567891011121314151617181920...","permalink":"/post/2025-12-14-01","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.7k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Go","slug":"Go","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Go.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Go","slug":"Go","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Go.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">上代码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Reverse","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"每一次的突破，都是自我超越的见证。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/hyhacct","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"PCL2下载","uid":"f6aaa4eee62482b760c88d2f20c35498","slug":"2025-07-18-16","date":"2025-07-18T17:59:06.000Z","updated":"2025-12-14T13:30:18.574Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2025-07-18-16.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/cover/Minecraft_1.png","text":"下载地址抗揍云下载地址: https://ltcat.lanzouv.com/b0aj6gsid 提取码: pcl2 ","permalink":"/post/2025-07-18-16","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":59,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Minecraft","slug":"Minecraft","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Minecraft.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"PCL2 Minecraft","slug":"PCL2-Minecraft","count":1,"path":"api/tags/PCL2-Minecraft.json"}],"author":{"name":"Reverse","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"每一次的突破，都是自我超越的见证。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/hyhacct","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"docker login失败问题","uid":"a77a7ec92bcb16dc214e2c5c8160b65b","slug":"2025-11-28-01","date":"2025-11-28T12:14:26.000Z","updated":"2025-12